parameters.name: Dimension
parameters.description:
The type of the parameter.   
Valid values: CLUSTER and TENANT.

parameters.name: DimensionValue
parameters.description:
The resource ID of the parameter type.   
You can leave this parameter unspecified when you call this operation to query the modification history of cluster parameters. In the case of tenant parameters, pass the tenant ID.

parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end time for the query of parameter modification history.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The ID of the OceanBase cluster.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description:
The number of the page to return.    
- Start value: 1   
- Default value: 1

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of rows to return on each page.   
- Maximum value: 100   
- Default value: 10

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The start time of the time range for querying the parameter modification history.
